FEATURES
========
v1
------------
search --- with non-ASCII: blase
main
my defs, examples, idioms
ask creating => finds create

new features
------------
tags - all_tags(), tags(word), addtag(word)
all words (for, related)
know = True

commands
------------
quit()
exit()
gedit()
idioms() -- add idiom for word.
adddef() -- add a definition, when I got smth clearer.
know()    (prev, see)  -- decide which definitions will be visible, and which not, for a word.
BETTER: mark(prev, markname)

explain(word, value) - find defs containing word
uses(word, value) - find examples containing word

myexplain(word, value) - find my defs containing word
myuses(word, value) - find my examples containing word
mine() - show a list of all words containing 'my' items
related(word) - all words whose definition word  / expression contains "word" or any derived forms thereof.
word(w) - search regular expression for a def word matching w. (for words in the liking of w).

